name: Roebuck
details:
MOSFET DistortionLook closely at the boards of top L.A. and Nashville players and you will see the 1990’s Ibanez® ­Mostortion™ again and again. Danelectro® brings back this awesome pedal, nailing the original tone and grit, but also adding 2 tasty ­clipping ­options. Better than ever!
